Package: scGAS
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Gene Activation Potential Inference via Reference Map
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Weiyan", "Chen", email = "weiyan.chen@bric.ku.dk",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: scGAS infers Gene Activation Potential (GAS) from single-cell
    ATAC-seq data using a bulk-tissue reference map of cCRE-Gene associations
    and Lasso regression models. It implements four main steps: (1) preprocessing
    scATAC-seq fragment files against reference cCREs, (2) training per-gene
    Lasso models on ENCODE bulk data, (3) computing and propagating scGAS scores
    to single-cell resolution via Metacells and network propagation, and
    (4) constructing and visualising the Chromatin Potential Field that links
    chromatin activation to transcriptomic state.
